<doc id="561570" wikidata="Q6246897" url="?curid=561570" title="John Marshall Law School">
<text>John Marshall Law School may refer to:
*Atlanta&#x27;s John Marshall Law School in Atlanta, Georgia
*Cleveland-Marshall College of Law in Cleveland, Ohio, now known as Cleveland State University College of Law
*John Marshall Law School in Newark, New Jersey, now known as Seton Hall University School of Law
*Marshall-Wythe School of Law in Williamsburg, Virginia, now known as William &amp; Mary Law School
