<doc id="561595" wikidata="Q6175406" url="?curid=561595" title="Jefferson Community College">
<text>Jefferson Community College may refer to:

* Jefferson Community College, now known as Jefferson Community and Technical College, a two-year Kentucky college 
* Jefferson Community College (New York), a two-year college located in Watertown, New York
* Jefferson Community College, later known as Eastern Gateway Community College, in Jefferson County, Ohio
* Jefferson Community College (Missouri), in Jefferson County, Missouri
* Jefferson State Community College, in Alabama</text><links>
